## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-102">下表顯示目前支援的選項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-103">分類</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-104">設定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-105">值/效果</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-106">Contract - 合約</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-107">繼承</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-108">`true` 若要開啟合約繼承;`false`將它關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-109">預設值為 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-110">執行階段</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-111">檢查</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="a10d1-112">`true` 若要開啟 執行階段檢查;`false`將它關閉。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-113">預設值為 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-114">您可以使用這個屬性，如下列範例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-115">若要關閉執行階段檢查整個組件：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-116">若要開啟執行階段合約檢查特定型別：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a10d1-117">若要關閉執行階段檢查的特定方法：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a10d1-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
